                            <comment id="17264090" author="beobal" created="Wed, 13 Jan 2021 11:46:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fix is really trivial, just an oversight in the handler which takes care of initial protocol negotiation. I&apos;ve added a unit test which checks the stream ids across the negotiation process for all supported versions. &lt;/p&gt;

